Create an empty chessboard using a 2D-array.
Create the white/black pieces with following attributes: color, type, position. pieceValue.
Place the pieces on the board according to the chess starting formation.
Implement movement of the pieces ba asking the user which piece shall move to what position.
Restrict movement, if other pieces are in the way of the piece you are moving.
Implement a method to capture pieces. (Use 2 separate arrays for captured pieces for black and white).
Display the captured pieces.
Display the pieces with actual image.
Implement special rules (en passant, castling, queening).
Implement win condition.
Implement draw-condition.
